{
  "name": "devsecops-agency",
  "version": "0.3.9",
  "description": "A fully autonomous AI software-development company in a plugin. You speak only to the CEO; the CEO runs a board of 16 Chiefs; each Chief runs a council of specialists; specialists may, when work shards cleanly, spawn workers to run in parallel. Research-first, security-second, receipts-always. STRIDE + OWASP Top 10 baseline for code; OWASP ASI Top 10 2025 via the Red-Team Council; every shipped artifact gets SBOM + SLSA provenance; DLP on every outbound tool call; secrets only via vault refs; runtime-hook enforcement of commit-gate, secrets-scanner, tool-guardian, governance-audit, dependency-license-checker, session-logger. 1 CEO + 16 Chiefs + 75 specialists = 92 agents; Audit / Evaluation / Red-Team / SRE are informing + independent — never on any project's delivery path. v0.3.9 'Rhythm+Career' — adds RHYTHM.md + CAREER.md at repo root and two new skills. RHYTHM.md declares 4 heartbeat cadences: daily (CEO, `heartbeat-<date>.md`), weekly (CEO+COO, `weekly-<YYYY-WW>.md`), monthly (CAO+CPO, `monthly-<YYYY-MM>.md`), quarterly (COO+CEVO+user, `quarterly-<YYYY-Q>.md`). State lives in `_vision/rhythm/state.json` with lastDaily/lastWeekly/lastMonthly/lastQuarterly + degradedCount; missed heartbeats escalate 1st miss → yellow compliance-drift, 2nd → ADR + Rung 2, 3rd → Rung 3 (blocks new projects). CAREER.md declares within-tier L1 (trial) → L2 (steady) → L3 (principal) ladder: L1→L2 needs 2 consecutive greens + ≥10 reports + zero roster-upgrade ADRs, L2→L3 needs 4 consecutive greens + ≥3 stepping-stones + ≥1 mentor upgrade + zero high+ red-team, L3→L2 on any red or high+ finding, L3→L1 forbidden. Inter-tier mobility stays USER-ONLY (VALUES §10). Reserved names (CEO + 16 Chiefs + skill-creator) always L3. Two new skills: rhythm/ (heartbeat orchestrator invoked at session start + on schedule, 8-step process, composes with keeper-test on quarterly), career-ladder/ (per-agent level engine, quarterly sub-step of rhythm + ad-hoc on stepping-stone / mentor events, bootstrap writes every non-reserved agent at L1). CEO SKILL.md now runs the rhythm heartbeat at session start right after MISSION+VALUES+LESSONS; AGENTS.md + skills/AGENTS.md updated with 11 new anti-patterns + 2 new skill-index rows. Skill-layer and root-doc-layer only — no new agents, no new councils, no new tool grants. Foundation for v0.4.0 Governance+Resilience. Full wave-by-wave history (v0.2.0 → v0.3.8) is in CHANGELOG.md.",
